data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming four bedroom, two full bath cape cod style home. Nestled on a quiet street, this  residence boasts a prime location near restaurants, shopping, and schools. Enjoy the spacious interior with an updated kitchen and turn key readiness. The expansive backyard features new deck, an above ground pool, providing a private oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Embrace the ideal combination of a tranquil neighborhood and proximity to amenities in this inviting family home
